14:38.143 --> 14:40.145
Smuggling cocaine?

14:40.145 --> 14:41.947
That's got to be illegal,
peggy.

14:42.281 --> 14:44.283
Well, I thought
it was boggle sand.

14:44.783 --> 14:47.786
Now he's making
all kinds of demands.

14:47.786 --> 14:51.290
"one box of pornography,
