they always crumble.

15:39.254 --> 15:40.756
This is hank hill.

15:40.756 --> 15:42.758
You, huh?

15:42.758 --> 15:44.259
Well, you're not getting
any more

15:44.259 --> 15:45.761
of your funny timer sand

15:45.761 --> 15:48.764
and you're gonna
leave my wife alone.

15:48.764 --> 15:49.632
Uh-huh.

15:49.632 --> 15:54.136
No, your ass is mine
because we've got a plan.

15:54.136 --> 15:56.639
Sure we do.
It's a terrific plan.

15:56.639 --> 15:59.642
We discarded
2 perfectly good plans

15:59.642 --> 16:02.728
when we came up
with this great one.

16:02.728 --> 16:05.731
Why didn't you tell me
about our terrific plan?

16:05.731 --> 16:07.650
Peggy, I made that up.

16:07.650 --> 16:10.319
And the other 2 plans?

16:10.319 --> 16:14.323
Uh, he says if he doesn't
get his coke by noon tuesday,

16:14.323 --> 16:16.709
he's gonna turn you in
just for fun.

16:20.329 --> 16:22.331
Look, just go to the warden,

16:22.331 --> 16:24.833
and tell him you were naiv
e and that wes tricked you.

16:24.833 --> 16:26.085
I can't.

16:26.085 --> 16:27.586
They made me
watch a short film

16:27.586 --> 16:30.756
about the danger
of smuggling things
in to the prisoners.

16:31.256 --> 16:33.592
It was called
don't be a mule.

16:33.592 --> 16:34.760
[crying]

16:34.760 --> 16:38.480
I even got 100% on the tes
t they gave me afterwards.

16:38.480 --> 16:40.983
Well, you can't smuggl
e any more drugs in,

16:40.983 --> 16:42.434
that's for sure.

16:42.434 --> 16:44.436
Hey, what would happen
if we just gave wes

16:44.436 --> 16:46.238
a brick of
regular timer sand?

16:46.238 --> 16:47.773
Well, we can't do that.

16:47.773 --> 16:49.274
He is going
to deal this batch

16:49.274 --> 16:50.776
to the aryan brotherhood.

16:50.776 --> 16:53.278
If they think he tried
to pull a fast one--

16:53.278 --> 16:55.581
They would make
a pincushion out of him.

16:55.581 --> 16:59.451
Unless he tastes it.

16:59.451 --> 17:03.122
He always
tasted the timer sand
when I brought it in.

17:03.122 --> 17:05.624
.
