anything of it at the time

17:05.624 --> 17:08.127
he always said
it was very good timer sand.

17:11.180 --> 17:12.181
"primo."

17:12.181 --> 17:13.182
[crying]

17:17.803 --> 17:21.807
well, it's 12:40.
I think you're in the clear.

17:21.807 --> 17:24.143
Well, maybe the phone
isn't working.

17:25.477 --> 17:28.230
Hank, there's no dial tone.

17:28.230 --> 17:31.150
Oh! Hello? Well, this is
the freakiest thing.

17:31.650 --> 17:33.652
I didn't even hear
the phone ring. I was just--

17:33.652 --> 17:37.156
Yes, warden, I understand.
I will be there.

17:40.325 --> 17:44.413
Ok. He wants me to come in
and explain myself tomorrow.

17:44.413 --> 17:47.416
Well, I guess I'd better
make bobby's lunch

17:47.416 --> 17:49.418
for the next
2 to 5 years.

17:49.418 --> 17:50.502
[crying]

17:50.502 --> 17:51.920
what's going on?

17:51.920 --> 17:53.338
huh?
Uh, nothing.

17:53.338 --> 17:56.475
Hey, who's in the mood
for some fun?

18:00.179 --> 18:01.680
[arcade machine zapping]

18:01.680 --> 18:03.899
[arcade machine beeping]

18:03.899 --> 18:06.685
look, mom, gilda's
trapped in a fortress,

18:06.685 --> 18:07.986
but I'm gonna break her free.

18:12.024 --> 18:13.525
[both grunting]

18:14.993 --> 18:16.278
[sighs]

18:16.278 --> 18:19.782
oh, my sweet, swee
t little boy.

18:19.782 --> 18:23.786
.
Uh, peggy, i, uh..

18:23.786 --> 18:25.871
How're you set
for quarters?

18:25.871 --> 18:29.374
No, that's--that's not
what I meant to say.

18:29.374 --> 18:31.627
Uh, look, you said
the other day

18:31.627 --> 18:33.929
you've never had
a positive impact
on anybody's life.

18:34.296 --> 18:36.799
Well, I want you to know
that you have.

18:36.799 --> 18:39.551
I-i'd hate to think
where bobby, luanne, and I

18:39.551 --> 18:41.019
