18:43.472 --> 18:44.473
[sighing]

18:46.975 --> 18:49.778
come on. Those moles
aren't gonna
whack themselves.

18:52.364 --> 18:53.866
Uh, go!

18:54.867 --> 18:56.368
[moles squeaking]

18:57.870 --> 18:58.871
[crying]

19:00.372 --> 19:01.874
[crying]

19:03.826 --> 19:06.829
