it is my destiny
to be the nameless,

19:06.829 --> 19:08.831
faceless executioner.

19:08.831 --> 19:10.549
But do not fear me,

19:10.549 --> 19:13.552
for I am just part
of the circle of life.

19:13.552 --> 19:15.220
The last part.

19:15.554 --> 19:17.389
[laughing]
made you flinch.

19:17.389 --> 19:18.640
Lunch!

19:18.640 --> 19:20.642
[alarm ringing]

19:20.642 --> 19:22.144
[yelling]

19:36.441 --> 19:37.943
e
mrs. Hill,
did you smuggle cocain

19:38.443 --> 19:39.278
?
into my prison

19:41.747 --> 19:45.083
I came to this prison
to make an impact, to help.

19:46.418 --> 19:48.754
Help how?
By getting me hooked?

19:48.754 --> 19:50.873
Do you give all
your students drugs?

19:50.873 --> 19:53.292
That's not the right way
to motivate us.

19:53.292 --> 19:54.459
I never meant to--

19:54.459 --> 19:55.460
Tell him, peggy.

19:55.460 --> 19:56.962
Tell him about
the boggle timer.

19:57.379 --> 19:58.630
Stop rushing me.

19:58.630 --> 20:00.432
Come clean.
Tell him the truth.

20:00.799 --> 20:02.301
I came here
to tell the truth.

20:02.301 --> 20:04.636
I would never dream
of telling anything else.

20:07.222 --> 20:08.223
[sniffing]

20:17.482 --> 20:20.903
I never saw this man
before in my life.

20:20.903 --> 20:23.405
And--and what I mean
by that is

20:23.405 --> 20:25.407
I did not bring him cocaine.

20:25.407 --> 20:27.709
I would like to please see
the evidence against me.

20:34.583 --> 20:37.085
But there's
no cocaine in there.

20:37.085 --> 20:39.972
.
In fact, it looks like
it's been licked clean

20:39.972 --> 20:42.975
well, I--I had a little bit
left this morning

20:42.975 --> 20:44.476
but this was
an important meeting.

20:44.977 --> 20:46.011
I wanted to be
up for it.

20:46.011 --> 20:48.814
So, this is the only
evidence against me?

20:51.183 --> 20:52.684
It should be enough.

20:54.186 --> 20:56.521
I didn't bring in a thing.

20:56.521 --> 20:59.024
I swear to god
she smuggled
cocaine in to me!

20:59.524 --> 21:02.494
So, uh, I guess
it's this convict's word

21:02.494 --> 21:03.996
against my wife's.

21:03.996 --> 21:06.365
Now, let's see.
Who can we trust?

21:06.365 --> 21:08.867
Peggy, have you ever
decapitated anyone?

21:09.368 --> 21:11.753
