How about you, wes?

21:11.753 --> 21:13.038
[growling]

21:13.038 --> 21:14.039
g
have you ever done anythin

21:14.539 --> 21:16.008
that caused
a man's head to come off?

21:17.259 --> 21:18.677
[gasping]

21:19.011 --> 21:20.212
[grunting]

21:20.212 --> 21:22.214
[wes screaming]

21:22.214 --> 21:23.715
[wes groaning]

21:28.687 --> 21:31.189
well, I guess
someone owes me an apology.

21:31.189 --> 21:32.691
I wouldn't
hold your breath.

21:32.691 --> 21:34.693
d
I don't think
wes even apologize

21:34.693 --> 21:36.194
