he killed.

21:36.194 --> 21:37.946
I was talking about you.

21:37.946 --> 21:40.065
Oh! I'm sorry.

21:40.065 --> 21:42.567
Well, do you even know
what you're apologizing for?

21:42.567 --> 21:45.570
No. I'm sorry,
but I don't.

21:45.570 --> 21:46.705
I accept.

21:47.205 --> 21:48.707
You apologized
because you said

21:48.707 --> 21:50.826
I couldn't take care
of myself, and I can.

21:50.826 --> 21:52.327
So there.
All right.

21:52.327 --> 21:54.329
I thought it had
something to do

21:54.329 --> 21:55.831
with the prison.

